American pop singer, Justin Bieber has moved on completely from Selena Gomez as he’s now confirmed and official with Sofia, Lionel Richie’s daughter.
The new couple who touched down in Japan together for Justin’s performance as part of his Purpose Album World Tour could not get each other off their Instagram account as each posted more pictures of the other.
The 22-year-od pop star further shared a photo of the couple sitting in the back of a car following a black-and-white snapshot that was shared a few hours ago by the love bird.

Sofia is 17-years-old and the younger sister to fashionista Nicole Richie.

